ebook.com/USD-Challenge-103297651036526/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們是一群香港人，熱血自由和民主。<br />\n<br />\n我們現正受到中國黨國體系的打壓，我們不希望在銀行的存款成為中資企業的貸款，助紂為虐；我們亦不相信港共政權並沒有透過外匯基金持有大量人民幣資產。<br />\n<br />\n對於一個連市民性命安危都無法保障的政府，我們不認為他們有能力捍衛龐大的聯繫匯率制度。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我們發起USD Challenge。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n「接受挑戰者，請到銀行或找換店換取至少1000蚊美元現鈔，拍照上傳至社交媒體，同時附上此段文字並標籤三名好友，向他們發起挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hongkongers embracing freedom and democracy.<br />\n<br />\nWe are currently oppressed by the China party state system. We don&rsquo;t want our deposits in bank becomes loans for Chinese enterprises. Such action is assisting tyrant to act brutally. Also, we don&rsquo;t believe that the communist regime in Hong Kong doesn&rsquo;t hold large portion of RMB assets through Exchange Funds. <br />\n<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t think that the Government is able to defend the huge Linked Exchange Rate System because the Government cannot even protect citizens&rsquo; lives.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, we launch USD Challenge.<br />\n<br />\nThe flow is as followed:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To those who accept the challenge, please go to banks or exchange stores, get at least $1000 USD cash, take a photo and upload to any social media. At the same time, attach this paragraph, tag three friends and challenge them.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"62436da3b41db677595ca3bb6bcc2cf16a7b16da","tid":1477901,"uid":288876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"遮打要人呀"},{"pid":"c46192fe4f17976092efe2be442863737dc5a823","tid":1477901,"uid":17110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b7ea2f5fee90c5c1d9cbd669e68f46df41d2e26","tid":1477901,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲 </span></span></div><br />\n黑社會無差別襲擊人，警方唔拉黑社會<br />\n警黑合作， 警署落閘， 999唔通，無人被檢控 <br />\n721元朗恐襲第27日: 無人被檢控， 無警停職， 施襲者逍遙法外，市民安全零保障<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵!<br />\n </div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 香港警方=黑社會， 香港警方=恐怖主義組織<br />\n香港人一世都唔原諒香港警察<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"c74d3e6bd08636358e1c24ed14db580a828a1585","tid":1477901,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 香港警方=黑社會=恐怖主義組織</span></span></div><br />\n811--黑 警假扮示威者掟磚同火魔法<br />\n811--尖沙咀 6名警察扮示威者 帶隊召黑衫人 帶頭燒警署<br />\n811--銅鑼灣 警察扮示威者射丫叉 混入人群搞事後表露身分制服旁人同時大量防暴增援<br />\n811--以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n811--北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 黑警假扮示威者掟磚同火魔法<br />\n香港警察濫用暴力及喬裝成示威者煽動並參與暴力<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"8b721424ed65669c72bb9274f84d27bf0ee76575","tid":1477901,"uid":288876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀 出緊尼"},{"pid":"e8076d0de828e9c6f9da921ae17c84070439ce5c","tid":1477901,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵<br />\n記者請日日問<br />\n</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"562e7181228f3b7414c53917e1863c42537cd25c","tid":1477901,"uid":288876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:24:01.000Z"